'''咽頭齒'''是[[鯉科|鯉科]]、[[胭脂魚科|胭脂魚科]]和一些其他魚類咽弓處的[[牙齒|牙齒]]。<ref name="Ref_">[http://www.iowadnr.com/fish/iafish/suckerf.html "Suckers ''Catostomidae''"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iowadnr.com/fish/iafish/suckerf.html |date=20080730041116 }}, [[Iowa_Department_of_Natural_Resources|Iowa Department of Natural Resources]]</ref> 不過除魚類之外，其他生物可能也有這種構造，例如海蠕蟲[[三部蟲門|三部蟲門]]下的''Meiopriapulus''中的一個新物種也有咽頭齒。<ref name=Park>{{cite journal |author=Park JK, Rho HS, Kristensen RM, Kim W, Giribet G |title=First Molecular Data on the Phylum Loricifera – An Investigation into the Phylogeny of Ecdysozoa with Emphasis on the Positions of Loricifera and Priapulida |journal=Zoolog Sci. |volume=23 |issue=11 |pages=943–54 |pmid= 17189906 |doi=10.2108/zsj.23.943|date=Nov 2006}}</ref>

[[翻車鲀科|翻車鲀科]]、[[石鲈科|石鲈科]]的魚類以及[[沙鳅属|沙鳅属]]下的一些物種例如[[皇冠沙鳅|皇冠沙鳅]]會用它們的咽頭齒摩擦產生一種獨特的聲音。<ref name=rocha2>Rocha, L. A., et al. (2008). [http://stri.si.edu/sites/publications/PDFs/Rocha_etal_Lessios_2008_Haemulon_phylogenetics.pdf Historical biogeography and speciation in the reef fish genus ''Haemulon'' (Teleostei: Haemulidae).] {{Wayback|url=http://stri.si.edu/sites/publications/PDFs/Rocha_etal_Lessios_2008_Haemulon_phylogenetics.pdf |date=20131217000255 }} ''Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution'' 48 918-28.</ref> [[胭脂魚|胭脂魚]]只有一排梳子狀結構的咽頭齒。<ref name=Filaman>[http://filaman.ifm-geomar.de/Summary/SpeciesSummary.php?id=12304 ''Myxocyprinus asiaticus'', Chinese sucker fish, Filamn.ifm-Geomar.de, 2006] {{Wayback|url=http://filaman.ifm-geomar.de/Summary/SpeciesSummary.php?id=12304 |date=20080623214315 }}, retrieved on: August 21, 2007</ref>

